data.description: Easy living in this ranch-style home in the convenient Eagleridge area. Everything on one level but room to expand in an unfinished basement, this features hardwood floors throughout the main level, vaulted ceilings and a skylight.  The convenient kitchen has a center island with granite, pantry, eating area and all appliances stay.  Enjoy the warmth of the living room fireplace and cool with central a/c.  The backyard is fully fenced. Front and back are handicap accessible or ramps can be dismantled.  This is a terrific location near shopping or highways for commuters.
